                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>During the course of the Wake Island Conference, October 15, 1950, President
                    Truman, General Mac Arthur, and others present discussed briefly the situation
                    in Indochina. For a record consisting of the substance of statements made at
                    that conference, see <ref target="frus1950v07#pg_948">volume VII, page
                    948</ref>.</p>
            </div>
